            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-text-primary]">LoRa Range Calculator</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-secondary] mb-6 max-w-3xl">
          Estimate your maximum line-of-sight range based on transmit power, antenna gain, and receiver sensitivity. Real-world range will be shorter due to terrain, buildings, and atmospheric conditions.
